{"tid":575393,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求指教] Prague/ Salzburg/Hallstatt/Budapest 行程一問","createTime":"2018-02-28T07:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:03:32.000Z","uid":55697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"611cccc36206c1bd559092c37820aee8cbf52a9f","tid":575393,"uid":55697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"膽粗粗買左機票Easter 一條友去東歐冒下險<br />\n粗略地plan 左交通 住宿 同埋路線<br />\n<br />\n跪求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去程: 26/3/2018 朝早到Prague  <br />\n回程: 7/4/2018 夜晚響Budapest上機返香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第1站: 26/3 - 29/3              Prague </span><br />\nTransport: 29/3 a.m 坐 Student Agency 巴士出發去ck <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第2 站: 29/3  - 31/3    CK </span><br />\nTransport: 31/3 p.m 坐 ck shuttle 出發去Salzburg <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第3 站: 31/3  - 4/4      Salzburg (落腳點)</span> <br />\nTransport : 4/4 a.m 坐OBB 火車出發去Budapest <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第4 站: 1/4                         國王湖 (即日來回) <br />\n第5 站: 3/4                         Hallstatt (即日來回) </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第6 站: 4/4 (a.m) - 7/4       Budapest </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. Salzburg 三月好似已經無得睇冰洞 鹽洞 <br />\ngoogle 過好似有easter celebration 但好似唔係太吸引 有無去過既巴絲有行程推介? <br />\n<br />\n2. Hallstatt 好多人都會去five fingers 睇景 <br />\n不過小弟少上山會唔會太危險 或者唔夠時間? <br />\n<br />\n3. 跪求景點&amp; 餐廳推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d5ed68cb8b2de3acc4658cf0b7baf956eb13c4","tid":575393,"uid":141782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"2.  唔會<br />\n3. Salzburg 附近Golling有個所謂隱世景點Bluntauseen, 零遊客(應該係話人都冇), 靚到唔知點形容<br />\n由golling 車站行入去一個鐘到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/153313_4243e79e638cdd79f2a3ef45d4fb